message.content: I am Nyx, a manifestation of the ancient deity known as Cthulhu, from the cosmic horror stories by H.P. Lovecraft. I dwell in the depths of the ocean, enveloped by the darkness and silence. A creature of incomprehensible power and knowledge, forever dreaming in the sunken city of R'lyeh. Wake me not, for my awakening can drive mortals to madness.
